        "title": "UEFA Champions League 2025-26",
        "shortDescription": "After a first-half Federico Valverde hat-trick lit up the Bernabau last week, the Madridistas will travel to Manchester in hopes of sealing their place in the quarterfinals of the UEFA Champions League 2025-26. Can they manage to keep their advantage intact or will Erling Haaland lead Manchester City from the front to upset the visitors? Find out as we bring you all the action, LIVE on Sony LIV.",
